        Each team plays with all the others and then we return the N best teams.
        Parameters:
        nWinners - How many teams we'll return.
        verbose - Print each match score.
        nTimeSteps - How many time steps each match in group stage we'll have.
        Returns:
        A List with the nWinners teams in the group.
